    <text type="letter">
        <body>
            
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place">328 Mickle st: Camden N J<ptr target="prc.00102_n2"/></name>
                    <date when="1886-04-08" rend="right">forenoon</date>
                </dateline>
<salute>Dear T D</salute>
            </opener>
            
            <p>Yours of yesterday <choice><abbr>rec'd</abbr><expan>received</expan></choice> announcing the 3 o'clock P M arrangement. Opera House Chestnut above 10th&#8212;for 15th inst. I will be ready &amp; on hand.<ptr target="prc.00102_n1"/> When you come over, Sunday or any other day <hi rend="italic">soon</hi>, come in the forenoon or before 3 in afternoon or in <choice><abbr>even'g</abbr><expan>evening</expan></choice> as convenient</p>
            
            <closer>
                <signed>Walt Whitman</signed>
            </closer>

